{"tid":1163801,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人生總會失去你無諗過會失去嘅人","createTime":"2019-05-20T16:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T16:23:43.000Z","uid":254154,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9ed9f4e2b028df8a11205088ca39fee9d6a8b960","tid":1163801,"uid":254154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T16:02:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">[長 借ac]</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">兩年前 係我最愛 <span style=\"color: gold;\">出軌嘅前男友</span><br />\n兩年後 係識六年 <span style=\"color: gold;\">最好嘅朋友</span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n最傷心個陣 <span style=\"color: red;\">係佢扶我起身</span><br />\n所以 我特別珍惜 多謝佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以令自己成長嘅朋友唔多<br />\n佢係唯一一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇住佢由懶散去到目標明確 實踐<br />\n令我<span style=\"color: red;\">反思自己人生方向</span> 做返打算<br />\n<br />\n每年 我地會<span style=\"color: red;\">一齊訂目標</span>去完成 <br />\n例如草幾錢 草唔到要請食buffet <br />\n<br />\n佢性格內向 但比我嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">意見好有建設性</span> <br />\n每次傾完計 都會覺得煩惱少d<br />\n<br />\n近兩年 因為我個人問題 令我地成日嗌交<br />\n無論點都好 我地都會<span style=\"color: red;\">互相道歉 和好</span><br />\n<br />\n有時<span style=\"color: violet;\">付出代價換取原諒</span> 在所難免</span><br />\n<br />\n佢試過<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">坐過山車唔比我叫出聲</span></strong></span>先原諒我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都試過叫佢<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">食舊超多芥末嘅羊排</span></strong></span>先原諒佢<br />\n<br />\n呢d<span style=\"color: violet;\">互相傷害</span>嘅情節 都係<span style=\"color: violet;\">禮尚往來</span>嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">最近 佢突然<span style=\"color: pink;\">消失已經三個月</span><br />\n無論我講咩 做咩 佢都唔再理我<br />\n我感覺 佢好似<span style=\"color: pink;\">唔再當我係朋友</span>一樣<br />\n同陌生人無異<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">「遲結婚要封大份人情比另一個 <br />\n有機會就一齊去芬蘭睇北極光 」</span></strong><br />\n</span></del><br />\n<br />\n係我以前想像過有佢嘅將來 </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[size=6]<span style=\"color: red;\">而家<br />\n<br />\n無哂</span>[/size=7]<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">其實 我最驚 唔係失去<br />\n只不過無諗過個個 係佢<br />\n無諗過  佢會連原因都唔講咁消失<br />\n更無諗過 我<span style=\"color: red;\">人生嘅遺憾 最後都係有佢..</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"2b32f3823249825221422702b9d281a91902f128","tid":1163801,"uid":6762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T16:07:03.000Z","msg":"原因係點你估唔估到？<br />\n無可能無啦啦消失<br />\n定佢自己個人私事？"},{"pid":"5eda1694c0778dad6fee0b0446ad0687041b44d7","tid":1163801,"uid":254154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b32f3823249825221422702b9d281a91902f128","tid":1163801,"uid":6762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T16:07:03.000Z","msg":"原因係點你估唔估到？<br />\n無可能無啦啦消失<br />\n定佢自己個人私事？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T16:23:43.000Z","msg":"原因有機會係 <br />\n<br />\n自從呢兩年前我分手後<br />\n<br />\n將對前男友嘅期望同要求都投射哂係佢身上<br />\n<br />\n令佢壓力大"}]}